<figureCitation id="27EB36D2BDB35874188C76B5FA3E3F38" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. The newly described Melicope balgooyi Appelhans, W. L. Wagner &amp; K. R. Wood. A Flowering branch B Leaf with detailed venation C Pistillate inflorescence [peduncle not shown in full length] D Single staminate flower. Based on K. R. Wood 9727 (PTBG, A-C) and K. R. Wood 9698 (PTBG, D)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10698" pageId="1" pageNumber="78">Figs 3</figureCitation>
